title: Lynda - Advanced Google Analytics 2017
description:
Do you want to generate better reports about your web traffic, and 
make more intelligent decisions about where to focus your 
marketing efforts? In this course, take an in-depth look at 
Google Analytics, and learn advanced techniques that can help you 
use this popular and powerful analytics tool to glean better 
insights. Instructor Adriaan Brits dives into SEO metrics, and 
explains how to conduct an SEO performance analysis. He also 
shows how to integrate Google Analytics with WordPress; use 
advanced features such as filters, views, and dimensions; build 
customized team reports; conduct a conversation rate 
analysis; and more.eeNote: This course picks up
